{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act37side_level_act37side_05_beg","storyGroup":"act37side","storySort":10,"storyDependence":"act37side_level_act37side_04_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"GO-5","storyName":"废铁与铆钉","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"战后由议会所支持的工人群体组建了伦蒂尼姆工业振兴协会，费斯特作为顾问开始重启科技研发以及协助城市重建。与此同时，资源短缺带来的矛盾却依旧存在。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act37side/level_act37side_05_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act37side_05","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":8,"next":10,"characters":["热情的工人","费斯特","洛洛","焦急的工人","维娜","忧伤的人","？？？","广播声","凯瑟琳","珀茜瓦尔","维多利亚士官","戴菲恩"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/63/Avg_bg_32_g4_ordnancefactory.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act28side/m_avg_saferoom_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"dialog","id":9},{"type":"animtext","id":10,"name":"group_location_stamp","style":"avg_both","pos":"-400,-200","block":"false","text":"<p=1>新奥克特里格区，小型载具厂</><p=2>1098年12月21日 6:13 P.M.</>"},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":11},{"type":"animtextclean","id":12},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":13},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":14},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":15},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的工人","text":"你们终于来了，队长！帮我看看这张蓝图，奥克和我争论，说设计全新的电能驱动分配阀简直多此一举。","id":17,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的工人","text":"可照我们所预想的，将来肯定会有越来越多的大家伙从我们工厂运到伦蒂尼姆的每一个地块！","id":18,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的工人","text":"要我说，就该提前做准备。","id":19,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的工人","text":"不然到时候，未来真正用上这些载具的家伙们发现载重和牵引力完全不够时，一定会转过头来骂我们这些老东西保守——","id":20,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的工人","text":"“都是些没远见的家伙！”我可不想挨这种骂！","id":21,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"别叫我队长了，虽然我们关系好，但大家已经不是自救军了。何况我们也都各自回到了自己的工厂。","id":23,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a4/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"况且，你觉得奥克真想不到这些？无非也是觉得能省就省。","id":24,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a4/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的工人","text":"......我当然知道，但怎么也不该给后辈添堵吧。","id":26,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4040_rockr_1#12$1","focus":"m","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"马丁叔，我当然理解你的心情。","id":28,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_4040_rockr_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"不过我们总得慢慢来嘛。可露希尔和我们分享了很多她捣鼓出来的无人机技术，我也想把这些新技术统统塞到我们新研发的四足载具里。","id":29,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_4040_rockr_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"可电力供应，如何自动化，这些都是我们现在头疼的问题。蓝图虽然好，但还是得先立足当下慢慢来呀。","id":30,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_4040_rockr_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"马丁叔，先按奥克的说法，弄一个基础版解决燃眉之急。","id":32,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2e/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"你的蓝图照旧提交给“伦蒂尼姆工业振兴协会”留档吧，别遗失了。","id":33,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2e/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"有议会的支持，工业振兴协会本就以战后恢复维多利亚技术在国际上的领先地位为目的，每一个新的想法都应该被尊重。","id":35,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a9/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的工人","text":"反正你是协会的顾问，你说了算。","id":37,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"唔，最近是不是大伙提的新点子太多了......感觉快审不过来了。","id":39,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2e/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4040_rockr_1#12$1","focus":"m","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"毕竟大伙都难得能切实感受到自己的家能因为自己的想法发生前所未有的改变，所以热情都很高。","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_4040_rockr_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"是啊，工厂的流水线，串联所有街道的快速轨道系统，以及保护整座伦蒂尼姆的城墙和城防炮。","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2e/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"我们可以靠自己的双手，把它们打造成我们想象中的样子。","id":45,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a9/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的工人","text":"哎，你们说别的我都认同，但别是你想象中的样子吧，费斯特。我真怕街道被你改造成大游乐园，所有人都绑在滑索上滑来滑去。","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"呃，那只是被否决的提案中让大家笑得比较开心的一个嘛，又不能代表我所有的点子。","id":49,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a9/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"说到这个，你们厂真的决定把奥克留在核心车间吗？毕竟我听说他以前在的厂和你们不是很对付。","id":51,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"每个工厂都有自己的技术机密，以前也有因为抢订单而互相看不顺眼的情况，对吧......","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_660_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的工人","text":"哈，这倒是。我们厂也不是所有工人都加入了自救军。","id":54,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的工人","text":"不过凯瑟琳既然能说服其他工厂一起加入协会互相分享技术，那我们也没什么好保留的——","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_660_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":56},{"type":"charslot","id":57},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":58},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":59},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"焦急的工人","text":"来人！来人帮忙！","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"焦急的工人","text":"马修先生被人打了！","id":62},{"type":"dialog","id":63},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":64},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":65},{"type":"charslot","id":66},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_bg_55_g6_dusklentiavenue.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":67},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":68},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":69},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":70},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"......我们曾经见过吗，先生？","id":72,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":73},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":74},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_659_1#1$1","posfrom":"200,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"2","id":75},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","afrom":"0","ato":"1","duration":"1.5","id":76},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":77},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":78,"musicid":1},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_659_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"忧伤的人","text":"不，算不上，议长阁下。","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_659_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"忧伤的人","text":"我叫马修，只是一个有间小工厂的商人，但眼下的日子让我不得不向您抱怨。","id":81,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_659_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1","focus":"l","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"你可以写信给议会，或者直接向工业振兴协会求助。我现在......有别的事情需要好好想想。","id":83,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_659_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"忧伤的人","text":"阁下，我联合停工的十余座工厂写给议会的信，恐怕已经被您搁置大半个月了。","id":85,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_659_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"部分工厂停工是议会已经表决通过的事情。你不该比我更清楚伦蒂尼姆的物流港口现在是什么情况吗？","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_659_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"忧伤的人","text":"但一座工厂的债务崩溃能压死萨迪恩区或者海布里区的几百个家庭。","id":89,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_659_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"忧伤的人","text":"我们只是想为自己争取一点小小的倾斜——哪怕是以私下的形式。","id":90,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_659_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"忧伤的人","text":"我们这些停工的工厂，工人们想从地下渠道买药都买不起。流水线上那些经验丰富的老工人，可比十台机器还值钱。","id":91,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_659_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"忧伤的人","text":"我相信我的工人们，他们能为这座城市做的事，还有很多。","id":92,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_659_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"忧伤的人","text":"与此同时，疗养院里大量珍贵的矿石病抑制剂被分配给了那些半死不活的伤兵。","id":93,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_659_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"......你想说什么！","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fa/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_659_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"忧伤的人","text":"我想帮您算一笔“经济账”——","id":97,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_659_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"*维多利亚粗口*！","id":99,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fa/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":100},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_punchsp4","volume":"1","id":101},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"50,0","duration":"1","id":102},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"0.5","id":103},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"0.5","id":104},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":105},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":106},{"type":"playsound","key":"$fightgeneral","volume":"1","id":107},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":108},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0.5","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":109},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":110},{"type":"text","text":"维娜反应过来的时候，拳头已经砸在了对方的鼻梁上。","id":111},{"type":"text","text":"那个叫马修的男人一只手捂着流血的鼻子，另一只手狼狈地在口袋里寻找手帕。","id":112},{"type":"text","text":"可止不住的鲜血依旧从他的指缝间渗出来，染红了他的衣服。","id":113},{"type":"text","text":"周围越来越多的人围了上来，所有人都直勾勾地看着维娜。","id":114},{"type":"text","text":"他们并没有敌意或愤怒，只是每一道目光，都在提醒着维娜，她的无力，她的不合时宜。","id":115},{"type":"dialog","id":116},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"0.7","id":117},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#10$1","duration":"1.5","id":118},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_659_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":119},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":120},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"我——","id":122,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_659_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"忧伤的人","text":"我知道你为什么愤怒，阁下。我知道......但有些话，总得有人说。","id":124,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_659_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"忧伤的人","text":"说出这些话，对我来说，也并不好受。","id":125,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_659_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"忧伤的人","text":"我也曾是自救军的一员，一直留在城里，而你是跟着那个卡特斯女孩一起来的伙伴。后来，你们离开了。","id":126,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_659_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"忧伤的人","text":"等到典范军进城以后，我从凯瑟琳女士那里得知了你是他们的领袖，我没有任何犹豫就同意升起蒸汽欢迎你们。","id":127,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_659_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"忧伤的人","text":"但我第一次看到穿着国王的衣服站在街头，代表议会向大家承诺美好生活的那个人时，却没认出来是你。","id":128,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_659_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"忧伤的人","text":"你明明知道，有些许诺根本兑现不了。你在救下一些人的时候，也在牺牲一些人，不是吗？","id":129,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_659_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":130},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":131},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":132},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":133},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"100,0","duration":"0.8","focus":"l","id":134},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":135},{"type":"text","text":"她想要让男人闭嘴。","id":136},{"type":"text","text":"她轻松就抓起了男人的领子将他提了起来，可她看到了男人的眼睛，看到了周围所有人的眼睛。","id":137},{"type":"text","text":"“推进之王可以靠着拳头解决问题。”","id":138},{"type":"text","text":"她多希望只要拳头砸下去，问题依然会和过去一样轻松地被解决。","id":139},{"type":"dialog","id":140},{"type":"playsound","key":"$aluminum","volume":"0.5","id":141},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"5","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":142},{"type":"text","text":"有什么东西从她的口袋里掉了出来，在地上撞出一阵丁零当啷的响声。她很久没吃过糖了，都忘了这只铁盒一直都放在这套衣服里。","id":143},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_659_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"忧伤的人","text":"同意停工让出源石燃料的时候，我们都相信过你。但现在，我们只希望被牺牲的不是自己。","id":145,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_659_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"忧伤的人","text":"拳头没法解决所有事......“推进之王”。","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_659_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":147},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cnstrctnck","volume":"1","id":148},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":149},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1.5","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"5","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":150},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":151},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2.5","id":152},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"none","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......维娜！","id":154},{"type":"dialog","id":155},{"type":"charslot","id":156},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":157},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1","duration":"1.5","id":158},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"请放开马修先生。","id":160,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a4/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":161},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":162},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":163},{"type":"charslot","id":164},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/63/Avg_bg_55_g8_siegeoffice.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":165},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":166},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":167,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":168},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":169},{"type":"dialog","id":170},{"type":"animtext","id":171,"name":"group_location_stamp","style":"avg_both","pos":"-400,-200","block":"false","text":"<p=1>议长办公室</><p=2>1098年12月21日 7:32 P.M.</>"},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":172},{"type":"animtextclean","id":173},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":174},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":175},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":176},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"......还有，刚才马修先生的那些看法，不能代表其他工人。","id":177,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"啊，当然，我也不能。","id":179,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"我只知道，几个伙伴通过我搭上了罗德岛，想提高疗养院医疗设备的水平。我们没法凭空变出更多设备，但至少能让那些设备更高效。","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a4/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"......我想大多数工人还是全心全意地支持着当前的医疗系统运转的。","id":182,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a4/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"不，不该你来解释，费斯特，冲动的是我。","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/30/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"你们已经做到了所能做到的极限。","id":185,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/30/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"不断优化的医疗设备，重新启用的快速通行隧道，实验中的统一供暖系统......这座城市在短时间内的变化已经帮上了很多人。","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f9/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"那也多亏了你在议会帮我们挡了不少麻烦的同时还开了许多绿灯。","id":189,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2e/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"这本就是我的职责。凯瑟琳女士还好吗？","id":191,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"奶奶？","id":193,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"呃，以她的性格......就算我问她，她也什么都不会说。她就连咳嗽都会避免让人发现。","id":195,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/85/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"除此之外，她就和以前一样，虽然不用在工厂里干活了，但还是那么忙。我很少能见到她。","id":196,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/85/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"上个月我和她也有过一次这样的谈话。凯瑟琳女士就坐在这张椅子上，我邀请她加入议会，她拒绝了我。","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/30/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"还有你们在战争中瞒过萨卡兹耳目的秘密车间，以及里面保存的那件武器——","id":199,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/30/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"......现在的伦蒂尼姆用不上它。","id":201,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/85/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"的确，我和凯瑟琳女士在这件事上已经取得了共识。","id":203,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/30/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"只要你和凯瑟琳女士还能团结起绝大部分的工人，由你们自行看管那件武器不是坏事。","id":205,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f9/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"议会需要接受监督，我也需要。","id":207,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"......","id":209,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/85/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"如今的议会，没有多么成熟的系统，大部分人都在摸索，也总有人试图借议会之手做到些什么。","id":211,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"但他们迟早得明白，当初那个围绕着国王运作的议会早就不存在了。","id":212,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"是从国王被——呃——","id":214,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"不......他被吊死时，议会也并没有变化，无非是掌控者从国王变成了那几位公爵罢了。","id":216,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f9/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"直到最近，皇家科学院还活着的那些院士们才终于有机会重新整理完善了被打断的伦蒂尼姆城市志课题研究——","id":218,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"足足上百万字，院士们花费了半辈子来完善、修订，涉及了伦蒂尼姆的方方面面。","id":219,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"我从未想到，自己会从这个角度来重新认识自己的家乡。","id":221,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/30/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"也是从他们的报告里，我才第一次反应过来，这座城市的反抗，很早就开始了......","id":222,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/30/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"“萨卡兹实际把控城市之后，是还在城内生活的伦蒂尼姆人自发组织起来维持了绝大部分城市基础功能的运转，不论身份地位。”","id":224,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"院士们在报告里把这视作我们如今这个新议会的雏形。","id":225,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"......听上去有点......呃，强行？不过也挺有道理。","id":227,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/85/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"不，我看到的是另一件事，费斯特。战争时期为了活着，我们的确能暂时忘记所有的私心与分歧......","id":229,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f9/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"可现在，我说不准。","id":231,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"我甚至都没法保证自己能时刻保持理性。我需要有人能够拉住我，在我——","id":232,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"你希望是我们？","id":234,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/85/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"这就是我与凯瑟琳女士的约定。况且，我的剑不就是你们铸造后给我的吗？","id":236,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"这场战争摧毁了很多东西，伦蒂尼姆想要不在时代变革里落后，还需要你们帮忙。","id":237,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"虽然有时你们的天才点子会让议会和科学院审批的人很头疼，但这并非坏事。","id":239,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7c/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"嘿嘿。","id":241,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a9/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"完全属于我们自己的城防系统，长期被维多利亚公爵们忽视的自动化技术，以及蒸汽骑士时代结束后新的威慑武器......","id":243,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"无一不需要你们的协助。这些必须是为了伦蒂尼姆，而非任何具体的某个人。","id":244,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1","focus":"r","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"费斯特，我不值得你们的信任。现在的议会也还不值得......你如果去看望马修先生的话，再替我向他道一次歉。","id":246,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"我会继续向议会争取更多可以改善工人条件的政策。","id":247,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"向大公爵采购的药物已经在路上了，只要货运渠道的安全问题可以解决，情况很快就能好转。","id":248,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"呵，谁又敢威胁公爵们的运输舰？","id":250,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/76/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"......我会继续和公爵们安插在城里的代表们沟通。","id":252,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/30/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"如果有我们能帮上忙的地方，大伙儿随时都在。","id":254,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/85/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":255},{"type":"charslot","id":256},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":257},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":258},{"type":"text","text":"费斯特从桌边站起身，犹豫了片刻，还是没有走出去。","id":259},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"奶奶总是教训我太爱胡思乱想。","id":261,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"但我第一次从工业振兴协会带回大家提出的一堆创造未来的方案那天，她什么都没说。","id":262,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"没多久，她就以身体状况不好为借口，从流水线上退了下去。","id":263,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"......维娜，我们都不讨厌畅想未来。我们会挺过去的。","id":265,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/85/Avg_avg_4072_ironmn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":266},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":267},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"200,0","duration":"2","id":268},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1.5","id":269},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":270},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":271},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":272},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorclosequite","volume":"1","id":273},{"type":"delay","time":"3.5","id":274},{"type":"text","text":"办公室变得很安静。维娜望着桌面上堆积如山的文件，沉默良久，打开了收音机。","id":275},{"type":"dialog","id":276},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":277},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_button","volume":"1","id":278},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"广播声","text":"滋滋——","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"广播声","text":"......在今天傍晚，多位市民目睹了亚历山德莉娜·维多利亚议长阁下惩治小人的一幕。","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"广播声","text":"据称，一名绅士试图向议长行贿来为自己牟利，而议长本人用最直接的手段拒绝了对方。","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"广播声","text":"越来越多的市民认为，维多利亚议长阁下有充足的人格魅力，足以——","id":283},{"type":"dialog","id":284},{"type":"charslot","id":285},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_button","volume":"1","id":286},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":287},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1","duration":"1.5","id":288},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"......","id":290,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":291},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":292},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":293},{"type":"charslot","id":294},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_bg_27_g7_subway.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":295},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":296},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act28side/m_avg_saferoom_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":297,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":298},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":299},{"type":"dialog","id":300},{"type":"animtext","id":301,"name":"group_location_stamp","style":"avg_both","pos":"-400,-200","block":"false","text":"<p=1>伦蒂尼姆地下</><p=2>1098年12月21日 8:01 P.M. </>"},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":302},{"type":"animtextclean","id":303},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":304},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"看来我们之间总算是达成了一点信任。","id":306,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"无论你们是终于放心这条运输线可以单人押送......还是真的如你所说，大部分人离开了维多利亚。","id":308,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":309},{"type":"charslot","id":310},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":311},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":312},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"可你还是带着你的小机器，我没看出你对我有多信任。","id":314,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"城里到处都是走投无路的难民，我得保证物资不被人抢走。","id":316,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"当然，我从没说过你们不是威胁的一部分。","id":317,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"但在伦蒂尼姆，知道整合运动过去凶名的人其实没那么多。","id":319,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"你清点一下吧，交易清单上的物资都在这里了。下一批药物我也会按时送到。","id":321,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"你说，你们中大多数人确实已经走了，那位九......？","id":323,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"她走了。或者说，她带着许许多多在这座城市里再也找不到家的人离开了。","id":325,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"当然，不影响我们在城外的工厂继续运转，你帮我们找的运输线路也能继续派上用场。","id":327,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"你不跟着他们走吗？现在的伦蒂尼姆，对感染者可算不上好地方。","id":329,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"“算不上好”，真像一个伦蒂尼姆人会用的委婉说法。","id":331,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"很小的时候，我确实好奇过故事书里的伦蒂尼姆——住着国王和小公主的皇宫花园，像迷宫一样适合探险的工厂。","id":333,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"不过后来我知道了，伦蒂尼姆和维多利亚别处也没什么不同。都不适合安家。","id":334,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"我没走只是因为总得有人留下来，我又比较喜欢做点踏踏实实的工作。况且，现在的伦蒂尼姆对感染者的态度......并不差。","id":336,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"是吗？","id":338,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"我跟着他们，只是因为他们救了我一命。我可不像一些同伴那样，做好了死的准备，想好了如何死得其所。","id":340,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"......何况最后，他们往往还是死得很不值。没有谁是该死的。","id":341,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"你也确实救了很多人，我得替工人们感谢你。","id":343,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"下次在城内塞传单的时候，可以顺路来海布里区做客。你那身伪装，我认得出。","id":344,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":345},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"......","id":346,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"货物我清点完了，没出差错。我就带着这些回去了。","id":348,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"等一下，凯瑟琳奶奶......","id":350,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"说吧。","id":352,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"......如果你身上长出石头的地方半夜会痛，我有一些能让自己好受点的小技巧。","id":354,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"我觉得你应该很清楚，我们能制造的药......效果并不如专业药企的那么好。","id":355,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":356},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"是。骗得了大部分工人，骗不了我自己。眼下在伦蒂尼姆流通的抑制药物，差不多都是这样。","id":357,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"但我这个年纪，剩下的清醒日子本来也不多，熬过的日子也不算少。","id":358,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4162_cathy_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":359},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"多清醒一天，多做一件该做的事，这就够了。","id":360,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4162_cathy_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":361},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":362},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":363},{"type":"charslot","id":364},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_bg_27_g7_subway.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":365},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":366},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":367},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":368},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维多利亚士官","text":"我们派过去的人已经追溯到了整合运动在城外的据点、两家主要的工厂和运输渠道。","id":370,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_422_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维多利亚士官","text":"要封锁这条通道吗？","id":371,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_422_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":372},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"......","id":373,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":374},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"不用。从目前的情报来看，他们对伦蒂尼姆市民的生活并无威胁。","id":375,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/de/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"维娜提起过，她对整合运动的警惕有个人的原因。","id":376,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/de/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"但她也承认，从明面上看，他们当时鼓动伦蒂尼姆市民对抗公爵的行为确实帮了我们大忙。","id":378,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":379},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"至于眼下的灰色贸易......只要确保它完全在掌控之中就行。珀茜瓦尔不是傻子，她知道什么不能碰。","id":380,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"整合运动的主要成员撤出伦蒂尼姆之后，整合运动的威胁并不高，保持关注就好。","id":381,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"甚至，如果大家都是想要改善感染者的问题，我们不介意和他们有私下的接触。","id":382,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":383},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维多利亚士官","text":"收到。我们会保持对整合运动的低强度监视。","id":384,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_422_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":385},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我知道，这样的工作对你们而言是一种大材小用。","id":386,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":387},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维多利亚士官","text":"——当然不会，戴菲恩阁下！","id":388,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_422_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"从离开温德米尔公爵的军舰开始，到接近伦蒂尼姆时停止情报活动一心突入，再到现在......","id":390,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":391},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":392},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"......你会想念丽茵卡登的湖水吗？","id":394,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":395},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":396},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":397},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":398},{"type":"charslot","id":399},{"type":"image","id":400}],"characters":["热情的工人","费斯特","洛洛","焦急的工人","维娜","忧伤的人","？？？","广播声","凯瑟琳","珀茜瓦尔","维多利亚士官","戴菲恩"]}